INSERT INTO `wefi_pages` VALUES (8,'about-us','About Us','Hello Sinahala','Hello Tamil','<h2>Who we are?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The xxx portal was developed under the Asian Development Bank&#39;s (ADB) &ldquo;Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises Line of Credit&rdquo; project supported by a grant from the &quot;Women Entrepreneurs Finance Initiative (We-Fi)&quot;. Through this project, we aim to empower women entrepreneurs in Sri Lanka by providing you with access to the necessary knowledge, skills, and support to improve your financial literacy, enhance your business management capabilities and grow your businesses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As our key regulatory stakeholder, the Ministry of Finance (Department of Development Finance) oversees the implementation of this project in Sri Lanka. We have also partnered with 10 major banks in Sri Lanka, as our partnering financial institutions under this project.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can see further details about our partners under the &quot;Our Partners&quot; section at the bottom of this page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What do we do?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>We know you dream of making it big one day. We are here to help you achieve that dream.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our goal is to support the capacity development of micro, small and medium enterprises (MSMEs), in particular women-led MSMES, by providing ease of access to relevant and up-to-date information and resources to support your business growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide support in the following areas:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Learning&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Mentoring</li>\r\n	<li>Networking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The resources in this portal are aimed at enhancing your entrepreneurial skills and management practices, help in making better decisions, develop your businesses, and achieve your dreams of success!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Who is it for?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you a woman who already owns/ manages or plans to start a micro, small or medium-sized business, then this portal is for you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"register\">Click here to register</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternatively, if you are a subject matter specialist in any business-related area, a successful entrepreneur who would like to share your learnings with others, or a professional with industry experience, you may like to volunteer as a mentor to our entrepreneur community.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><strong>I am not a woman entrepreneur. Can I join?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, you can. Many of the resources in this portal, such as learning materials and networking opportunities, will be useful to all MSME entrepreneurs and aspiring entrepreneurs. However, women entrepreneurs will have access to content targeted towards their interests and/ or additional services through the portal.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n','','<p>Hello Tamil</p>\r\n'),(9,'learning','Learning','','','<p>Managing a business is not just about buying and selling. The business world is constantly changing, and it is vital to gain the right knowledge and skills in order to stay ahead of the competition and grow. However, as entrepreneurs with a full-time commitment to running a business, finding the time is often a challenge. The xxx portal offers easy access to a range of learning resources useful to micro, small, and medium-sized entrepreneurs, with the flexibility to learn anywhere, anytime.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are at the start-up, growth, or mature stage of your business, browse through our resources to enhance your business know-how, stay updated on industry news and insights and get a quick and easy guide to find the right information for your specific business needs. Once you are a registered user, you also have the opportunity to engage in our self-learning resources, prepare your own training calendar, mark your favorite lessons, and track your progress on your personalized dashboard. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://128.199.181.107/learning-materials.php\">Learning Materials</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://128.199.181.107/tools-formats.php\">Tools and Formats</a></li>\r\n	<li>Success Stories</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','','');
